org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.HRM.HwLogical.HwTiming

Interface HwTimer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, HwResource, HwTimingResource, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, TimingResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HwTimerImpl

    public interface HwTimer
extends HwTimingResource
    A representation of the model object 'Hw Timer'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Nb Counters
    • Counter Width
    • Input Clock
    See Also:
    HwTimingPackage.getHwTimer()
